  "detailed_description": "<h1>Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/e01cf3df17cc111ac2ed9d318f76d9c4.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/e01cf3df17cc111ac2ed9d318f76d9c4.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/e01cf3df17cc111ac2ed9d318f76d9c4.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blobs in Space!</h2>Prepare for an intergalactic showdown like never before in Armed and Gelatinous: Couch Edition, the ultimate multiplayer party game that pits friends and family against one another in a fast-paced cosmic brawl. Dash to victory in a multitude of fully customizable battle modes. Customize matches and unleash chaos with a fully loaded arsenal of lethal weaponry, including an impressive selection of firearms, rockets, lasers, and melee blades.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/bb80e0f1811e94256ed6925cb0740d4b.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/bb80e0f1811e94256ed6925cb0740d4b.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/bb80e0f1811e94256ed6925cb0740d4b.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect, Grow, and Fight!</h2>With each weapon collected, your blob's girth increases along with your destructive power! Although becoming a massive blob also provides you with a bigger health bar, you suffer a significant loss in speed and agility. Smaller blobs can more easily dodge bullets and evade attacks plus their supercharged Dash Attack has a much longer range. Less is more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/c1ae8f19c4aba17537b3adf8228e569b.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/c1ae8f19c4aba17537b3adf8228e569b.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/c1ae8f19c4aba17537b3adf8228e569b.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dodge, Pass, and Score!</h2>Team up and throw down in a variety of high-energy sports minigames including Blob Soccer, Dodgeball, and Football!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/4a649451b9c8d0875f8cd647227f5ee7.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/4a649451b9c8d0875f8cd647227f5ee7.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/4a649451b9c8d0875f8cd647227f5ee7.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Armed and Gelatinous: Couch Edition is perfect for your next shindig, get-together, or soiree!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keep the party going with 9 Unique Game Modes<br></li><li>Become Unblobable with 16 Lethal Weapons<br></li><li>Spice up matches with 6 Special Item Crates<br></li><li>Dash across the galaxy in 16 Different Levels<br></li><li>Earn 21 Unlockable Bonuses, from weapons to game modes<br></li><li>Challenge friends or take on AI opponents with 5 CPU Difficulty Levels<br></li><li>Jam out to 21 Tasty Tracks from 8 incredible artists on the A&G OST</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/754a989409b1fd6439343ec299fd9038.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/754a989409b1fd6439343ec299fd9038.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/754a989409b1fd6439343ec299fd9038.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2>Personalize matches however you like in a variety of game modes:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Death Match - First to get the target score wins!<br></li><li>Time Match - Best score at the buzzer wins!<br></li><li>Stock Match - Last blob standing!<br></li><li>Combo King - Keep that combo going!<br></li><li>Blob Dojo - Sandbox mode to get swole!<br></li><li>Blob Soccer - Dash Attacks are fair game!<br></li><li>Blob Bombardment - Dodgeball with Cannons!<br></li><li>Blob Blitz - Think Football but faster!<br></li><li>Food Fight - Grab the most tacos to win!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/9a8888b72cde3413463dcd2b5fc05ce8.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/9a8888b72cde3413463dcd2b5fc05ce8.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/9a8888b72cde3413463dcd2b5fc05ce8.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize Matches!</h2>Customize each match by setting the target point count, timer length, or number of lives! An unlockable arsenal menu allows you to choose from a multitude of weapon loadouts where you can set up insane matches like Rockets Only (our personal favorite) or disable all weapons for Dashers Only!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/893bc49bb11b59273efe299a096aad13.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/893bc49bb11b59273efe299a096aad13.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/893bc49bb11b59273efe299a096aad13.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Jelly Jams!</h2>Armed and Gelatinous: Couch Edition also features an Original Soundtrack showcasing 21 outstanding tracks from 8 brilliant artists including Chris Huelsbeck, Poul O’Rourke, and Zac Zinger, in addition to a symphony of expertly crafted sound effects from legendary sound designer, Jory Prum.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/e5176d8abe5d1d5ebdf2e6933ef9e26a.poster.avif?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/e5176d8abe5d1d5ebdf2e6933ef9e26a.webm?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/e5176d8abe5d1d5ebdf2e6933ef9e26a.mp4?t=1758214623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/446510/extras/25292b923fdf1ce9e001af446824da5d.webp?t=1758214623\" width=600 height=30 /></span>",
